- 0.2.7
    - Added ability to align form button

- 0.2.6
    - Added ability to define form templates to offer the user a choice field.
        - To get this to work add the following to your settings file:
            FORM_TEMPLATE_CHOICES = (
                ('standard', 'Standard'),
                ('path/to/custom/template.html', 'Styled Template'),
            )
    - Added the ability to display form title above form fields

